theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;贝尔金&lt;/a>; 等。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;44wxsc&quot; >;下面，我们汇总了您可以找到的最佳 Apple 优惠...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23971262/black-friday-2023-apple-deals -网络星期一&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23971262/black-friday-2023-apple-deals-cyber-monday" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23971262/black-friday-2023-apple-deals-cyber-monday</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry><entry><published>2023-11-27T09:15:58-05:00</published><updated> 2023-11-27T09:15:58-05:00</updated><title>网络星期一最佳优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;网络星期一用手机购物的人的明亮彩色矢量插图&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/dsf1GiP4Phn-ykVroKnHQ8R1ieQ=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873 /cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/72905335/236878_CYBER_WEEK_DEALS_AFernandez.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;Aaron Fernandez 为 The Verge 绘制的插图&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;hw6L8a&quot; >;长假周末后的星期一毫无乐趣，除非您想省钱。如果您错过了黑色星期五的所有超值优惠，那么“网络星期一”为您提供了在假期前节省大量现金的又一个机会。 &lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;div id=&quot;idm7Ct&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;aside:11906226&quot;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/div >;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;bZLjoB&quot;>;例如，您仍然可以在购买许多受欢迎的礼物时获得大幅折扣，包括&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/Bose-QuietComfort -Wireless-Cancelling-Headphones/dp/B0CCZ1L489?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Bose QuietComfort Ultra 耳机&lt;/a>; 和 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www. amazon.com/Introducing-sound-compact-speaker-Lavender/dp/B09ZXJDSL5/?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Amazon 的 Echo Pop&lt;/a>; 到 &lt;a href =“https://www.anrdoezrs.net/links/8532386/type/dlg/sid/verge/https://www.sonos.com/en-us/shop/roam”rel =“赞助nofollow noopener”目标=&quot;_